data.description: Beautiful, quiet, perfect first home! This cute little home is located in a quiet neighborhood. It's location makes it a peaceful place to have outdoor gatherings, birthday parties, etc. The home is easily accessible and close to town, but far enough from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. The home includes two large bedrooms and large bathrooms, has an open floorplan which makes the home enjoyable and spacious. The property includes a creek along the back side of the property that is easily accessible. If you want a large yard to fence in for your pups this is the yard for you! The home has been well maintained and loved. The neighborhood is quiet and safe for children of all ages to enjoy playing outside. The home also includes a small storage shed with a lean-to attached for all storage needs. The owners installed a brand new heating and air system in June of 2018 and runs like a dream. The master bathroom was being painted and will be finished before selling. The home is being sold as is.
